sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from 'react' import { Img, Link, Logo, StyledAppBar, StyledButton, StyledIconButton, StyledNavLinks, StyledNavMobile, StyledToolbar } from './styles' import { TiThMenu } from 'react-icons/ti' import logo from '../../assets/logo.svg' import { Dialog, DialogActions, DialogContent, DialogTitle } from '@material-ui/core' const Navbar = () => { const [open, setOpen] = useState(false); const handleMenuOpen = () => { setOpen(true); }; const handleMenuClose = () => { setOpen(false); }; return ( Leiturama Menu Planos Benefícios Como Funciona Planos Benefícios Como Funciona Assinar ) } export default Navbar
